OL,3,CResearchers reach milestone in
OL,4,Cscreening of newborns for rare disorder
OL,6,FResearch midwives at University
OL,7,FHospitals Dorset have reached an
OL,8,Fimportant milestone in their screening
OL,9,Fof newborns for rare disorder spinal
OL,10,Fmuscular atrophy. (SMA)
OL,12,F1000 babies have now taken part in the
OL,13,Fscreening - using the same blood
OL,14,Fsample taken for the standard day-five
OL,15,Fnewborn test.
OL,17,FScreening for SMA as part of this test
OL,18,Fis already standard practice in many
OL,19,FEuropean countries, Australia and
OL,20,FNorth America.
