OL,3,CResearchers reach milestone in
OL,4,Cscreening of newborns for rare disorder
OL,6,FThe research aims to detect the
OL,7,Fgenetic disease after birth, before
OL,8,Fsymptoms develop, so babies can
OL,9,Freceive early treatment.
OL,11,FThe Trust is inviting women who are
OL,12,Fmore than 18 weeks pregnant, or who
OL,13,Fhave given birth in the last 28 days
OL,14,Fto get involved.
OL,16,FAffecting approximately 1 in 10,000
OL,17,Fbirths, SMA is a genetic disease that
OL,18,Fprogressively, and irreversibly,
OL,19,Fdestroys the nerve cells in the brain
OL,20,Fand spinal cord that control movement.
