OL,3,CResearchers reach milestone in
OL,4,Cscreening of newborns for rare disorder
OL,6,FCurrently in the UK, babies are not
OL,7,Fdiagnosed with SMA until they start to
OL,8,Fexhibit symptoms by which time
OL,9,Firreversible nerve damage and muscle
OL,10,Fweakness has occurred
OL,12,FIn children with the most common and
OL,13,Fsevere type of SMA, 95% of all motor
OL,14,Fneurons can be lost before the age of
OL,15,Fsix months.
