OL,3,CResearchers reach milestone in
OL,4,Cscreening of newborns for rare disorder
OL,6,FMost children with this type of SMA,
OL,7,Fif untreated, are unlikely to survive
OL,8,Fbeyond two years of age without
OL,9,Fpermanent ventilator support. Many
OL,10,Fchildren who survive will not be able
OL,11,Fto sit or walk independently.
OL,13,FBut there are treatments for SMA that
OL,14,Fhave been shown to benefit children
OL,15,Fwith certain types of SMA who are
OL,16,Ftreated at an early stage.
OL,18,FThe treatments have been approved by
OL,19,FUK regulatory bodies and can be given
OL,20,Fon the NHS.
