OL,3,CResearchers reach milestone in
OL,4,Cscreening of newborns for rare disorder
OL,6,F"Research plays a vital role in
OL,7,Fmedical science, and our maternity
OL,8,Fresearch team is proud to be involved
OL,9,Fin a study that strives to provide the
OL,10,Fvery best care for parents and their
OL,11,Fbabies, making a profound difference
OL,12,Fto families all over the UK.
OL,14,F"As midwives and parents, we normally
OL,15,Fonly see the babies for the first few
OL,16,Fweeks of their lives.
OL,18,F"This makes it very special for us to
OL,19,Fbe involved in something that could
OL,20,Fhave a longer term impact on the
OL,21,Fbaby's future."
